Kita ke Gastown sekarang!

809
01:53:44,385 --> 01:53:46,720
Dia tidak di Gastown.

810
01:53:48,555 --> 01:53:50,782
Di mana Praetorian Jack?

811
01:53:51,642 --> 01:53:53,077
Di mana War Rig kami?

812
01:53:53,101 --> 01:53:55,495
- Dia mendapatkan Bullet Farm.
