828
01:54:26,593 --> 01:54:28,099
Atau pilihan kesatria,

829
01:54:28,123 --> 01:54:30,488
Pergi ke Gastown dan hancurkan dia!

830
01:54:30,513 --> 01:54:32,198
Ini pilihanku!

831
01:54:32,224 --> 01:54:34,726
Kita buat dia berpikir
kita pergi ke Gastown.

832
