01:57:40,162 --> 01:57:42,879
<i>Perang 40 Hari Wasteland.</i>

855
01:58:01,141 --> 01:58:04,161
<i>Mata dibalas mata.</i>

856
01:58:04,227 --> 01:58:06,672
<i>Gigi dibalas gigi.</i>

857
01:58:09,149 --> 01:58:12,544
<i>Kemarahan yang digerakkan
